        "electron tomog" ;
    linkml:description "Three-dimensional (3D) reconstruction of single, transparent objects from a collection of projection images recorded with a transmission electron microscope. It offers the opportunity to obtain 3D information on structural cellular arrangements with a high resolution." ;
