    linkml:description "2 alleles of G12D mutation in KRAS gene. Mutation of KRAS, p.Gly12Asp (c.35G>A), Homozygous (PubMed=8026879, PubMed=11115575, PubMed=11169959, PubMed=11787853, PubMed=15367885, PubMed=21607521, Cosmic-CLP, DepMap)." ;
