<https://w3id.org/synapse/nfosi/vocab/Atypical%20MPNST> linkml:description "An intermediate-grade malignant peripheral nerve sheath tumor with atypical features that place it between benign neurofibroma and high-grade MPNST. Characterized by increased cellularity, nuclear atypia, and low mitotic activity." .

