    linkml:description "Astrocyte-like radial glial cell that extends vertically throughout the retina, with the nucleus are usually in the middle of the inner nuclear layer. [ http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21911394 GOC : NV ]" ;
