        <https://w3id.org/synapse/nfosi/vocab/absent%20clinically%20-%20no%20MRI>,
        <https://w3id.org/synapse/nfosi/vocab/present>,
        <https://w3id.org/synapse/nfosi/vocab/unknown> .

