        "Institution or person responsible for collecting, managing, distributing, or otherwise contributing to the development of the resource. Expects properly formatted name of the organization or person (e.g. \"NF-OSI\" or \"Robert Allaway\"), not an id. See https://datacite-metadata-schema.readthedocs.io/en/4.5/properties/contributor/." ;
