    linkml:description "Scientific characteristics: The species from which sample data were derived. If you are unsure or cannot find the appropriate term, please use 'Unknown' and email nf-osi@sagebase.org for help.",
        "Species of the organism(s) from which the data were generated. Omit property if not applicable, such as for data like compounds or other non-biological data.",
        "The name of a species (typically a taxonomic group) of organism." ;
    linkml:domain_of <https://w3id.org/synapse/nfosi/vocab/AnalysisResultTemplate>,
        <https://w3id.org/synapse/nfosi/vocab/AnimalIndividualTemplate>,
