    linkml:definition_uri "https://w3id.org/synapse/nfosi/vocab/AffinityProteomicsTemplate"^^xsd:anyURI ;
    linkml:description "Template for affinity-based proteomics data including antibody arrays (RPPA) and aptamer-based platforms (SomaScan). For antibody-based assays (RPPA), provide antibodyID. For aptamer-based assays (SomaScan), provide proteomicsPanel, panelVersion, and normalizationMethod." ;
