        <https://w3id.org/synapse/nfosi/vocab/BiologicalAssayDataTemplate_species>,
        <https://w3id.org/synapse/nfosi/vocab/BiologicalAssayDataTemplate_tumorType>,
        <https://w3id.org/synapse/nfosi/vocab/Component>,
