        <https://w3id.org/synapse/nfosi/vocab/workflow>,
        <https://w3id.org/synapse/nfosi/vocab/workflowLink> .

<https://w3id.org/synapse/nfosi/vocab/SpatialTranscriptomicsSequencingTemplate> a linkml:ClassDefinition ;
