        <https://w3id.org/synapse/nfosi/vocab/antibodyID>,
        <https://w3id.org/synapse/nfosi/vocab/comments>,
        <https://w3id.org/synapse/nfosi/vocab/geneticReagentID>,
        <https://w3id.org/synapse/nfosi/vocab/nf1Genotype>,
        <https://w3id.org/synapse/nfosi/vocab/nf2Genotype>,
