        <https://w3id.org/synapse/nfosi/vocab/ageUnit>,
        <https://w3id.org/synapse/nfosi/vocab/aqueductalStenosis>,
        <https://w3id.org/synapse/nfosi/vocab/attentionDeficitDisorder>,
        <https://w3id.org/synapse/nfosi/vocab/breastCancer>,
        <https://w3id.org/synapse/nfosi/vocab/cafeaulaitMacules>,
        <https://w3id.org/synapse/nfosi/vocab/dermalNeurofibromas>,
